short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Soroco Scout browser extension is a part of Scout agent (Soroco IP) installation

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Soroco customers who installed Scout agent need to enable this extension to collect their chrome interaction information.

Note:
To install Scout agent, you'll need to purchase a license from Soroco. 
For further information reach out to us at scoutsupport@soroco.com
